Enum Class MyPages

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<MyPages>
application.framework.MyPages
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<MyPages>, Constable
public enum MyPages extends Enum<MyPages>
Enum representing all the page routes in the application.

Each entry in this enum corresponds to a route string that is used to navigate between different pages. The routes are used by the PageRouter for page navigation.

Author:
Dhruv
